Revision History for dtddiff
-----------------------------
	@(#) dtddiff.CHG @(#)
==============================================================================
1.2.1   (Oct 09, 1996)

    Fixes:

	o -compact is NOW the default.

==============================================================================
1.2.0	(Aug 21, 1996)

    Changes:

	o -compact is the default.  -nocompact has been added to
	  provide a long listing.

	o -catalog has replaced -mapfile.

	o The only default catalog(s) file is "catalog" and no
	  longer "map.txt".

    Fixes:

	o dtddiff will now properly recognize the SGML_CATALOG_FILES
	  envariable.

==============================================================================
1.1.0	(Dec 08, 1995)

    Enhancements:

        o Entity map file syntax has changed to the SGML open catalog
          format (see CHANGES.dtd.pl).

        o Support for the envariable SGML_SEARCH_PATH (see
          CHANGES.dtd.pl).

        o Support for the envariable SGML_CATALOG_FILES (see
          CHANGES.dtd.pl).

==============================================================================
1.0.2	(Dec 16, 1994)

    Bug fixes:

	o Infinite loop occured when the -compact option was *not*
	  specified.  This has been been fix.


==============================================================================
1.0.1	(Dec 14, 1994)

    New Functionality/Enhancements:

	o Added -compact option which makes new/old elements/attributes
	  listed in 2 columns.


==============================================================================
1.0.0	(Dec 12, 1994)

    First release.

==============================================================================
